---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Quality Control AI">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="relative h-[300px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://www.ripik.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anomaly-Detection_1-1024x576.png" 
        alt="Quality Control" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Quality Control AI</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <h2>AI-Powered Quality Inspection</h2>
      <p>Our Quality Control AI system revolutionizes manufacturing quality assurance through real-time monitoring and defect detection.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Automated Parts Inspection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our advanced AI system monitors each part on the production line, identifying potential defects and deviations from specifications in real-time. This enables immediate intervention and maintenance of high quality standards.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65c37e39d15be5902352de08/65d6fd53c6b05058a53a62ab_ezgif.com-gif-maker%20(1)%20(2).gif" 
            alt="AI Parts Inspection" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://www.chooch.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ezgif.com-video-to-gif.gif" 
            alt="Inventory Tracking" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Intelligent Inventory Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The system tracks inventory movement and status in real-time, automatically updating data and optimizing logistics processes. This significantly reduces tracking errors and improves inventory management efficiency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>System Capabilities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time defect detection</li>
        <li>Automated quality grading</li>
        <li>Production line monitoring</li>
        <li>Detailed analytics and reporting</li>
        <li>Integration with MES systems</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>